            "body": "Esmor’s modular seating brings a bold, structured look defined by crisp geometry and tactile fabric finishes. Its sleek profile adds a refined, contemporary edge to any interior setting."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Supported by slim metal framing, Esmor adapts easily to different spatial needs. Its versatile layout transitions effortlessly across collaborative zones, reception areas, and informal meeting spaces.."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "High-quality upholstery paired with precise, timeless stitching delivers a sophisticated finish and long-lasting durability. The fine detailing enhances both comfort and visual appeal, maintaining a premium look even with everyday use."
          },
          {
            "heading": "",
            "body": "Crafted with robust metal legs, the design ensures excellent stability and strength while adding a sleek, contemporary touch. The elevated form enhances durability and complements modern workspace and lounge aesthetics."
          }
